snippet.title: Hypercharge: Unboxed - Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Hypercharge is a first and third-person shooter action figure game you've always dreamed of! Grab your friends, complete objectives, defend the Hypercore against waves of weaponized toys, and defeat Major Evil together in the story campaign! Hypercharge: Unboxed is coming soon to PlayStation 4 & 5. Wishlist now!

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
